The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Imo State Chapter, has blamed the failed road network in the state, on what it called “Chief Rochas Okorocha’s cruelty to Ndimo”.  A faction of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, in Imo State said they embarked on a sight seeing of Governor Rochas Okorocha’s projects in the state and discovered that “Okorocha is just setting a dangerous trap for Imolites.” November 30, 2016 In "News" Imo State chapter of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, says it is “shocked over the calculated attempt by Governor Rochas Okorocha’s administration to deny Imo pensioners their several months arrears of pension, through a well crafted fraudulent means.” December 28, 2016 In "News" The Imo State branch of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, has described Governor Rochas Okorocha's repeated attack on the party as "ludicrous irritating, falsehood and cheap political propaganda". June 29, 2017 In "News"